text: Hitler Wears Hermes IV is the third mixtape by American rapper Westside Gunn. It was released on October 31, 2016 through his own record label Griselda Records. ==Background== The mixtape includes guest appearances from Benny, Conway, Keisha Plum, Smoke DZA, Stalley and Tiona D. The album is produced by Daringer. ==Single== On August 30, 2016, the first single from the mixtape, "Mr. Fuji", was released. ==Track listing== All songs are produced by Daringer. ==References== Category:2016 mixtape albums Category:Albums produced by Daringer (producer)
title: Hitler Wears Hermes IV
